SubjectAddition to Musqueam Indian Reserve No. 2, British Columbia
PrecisOrder setting apart 3.14 hectares (7.76 acres) of land for the use and benefit of the Musqueam Indian Band as an addition to MUSQUEAM INDIAN RESERVE NO. 2, located almost entirely in the City of Vancouver, with a very small portion of the land located in the City of Richmond, British Columbia.
